fields.name: Wands
fields.description: The suit of Wands represents creativity and action.

fields.name: Cups
fields.description: The suit of Cups represents emotions and relationships.

fields.name: Ace of Wands
fields.reversed_meaning: Delays, lack of motivation, or missed opportunities.
fields.description: The Ace of Wands represents a spark of inspiration and creative potential.

fields.name: Two of Wands
fields.reversed_meaning: Fear of change, indecisiveness, or lack of planning.
fields.description: The Two of Wands symbolizes planning and taking the first steps.

fields.name: Three of Wands
fields.reversed_meaning: Delays, obstacles, or lack of progress.
fields.description: The Three of Wands represents progress and looking ahead.

fields.name: Ace of Cups
fields.description: The Ace of Cups symbolizes love and emotional fulfillment.

fields.name: Two of Cups
fields.description: The Two of Cups signifies partnerships and emotional connections.

fields.name: Three of Cups
fields.description: The Three of Cups represents joy and social connections.
